ğŸ”´ (1) Preorder + Postorder â†’ âŒ NOT POSSIBLE to construct a UNIQUE binary tree

   ğŸ“Œ Reason: Structure is not guaranteed.
   â–ªï¸ Multiple trees can have the same preorder & postorder.

   ğŸ” Example:
       Tree A:        Tree B:
