       â†’ Preorder = [9]
       â†’ Inorder = [9] â†’ Only one node â†’ leaf

   Step 4ï¸âƒ£: For right subtree:
       â†’ Preorder = [20, 15, 7]
       â†’ Inorder = [15, 20, 7]
       â†’ Root = 20
